<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:39:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>如果不解决社会问题，香港更严格的消防安全法就不会发挥作用</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/hong-kong-opinion/article/3259796/tougher-fire-safety-laws-hong-kong-wont-work-without-fixing-social-problems?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>新幸运屋发生的致命火灾造成 5 人死亡、43 人受伤，这表明消防安全法如果不得到执行，就无法拯救居民。虽然修订《消防安全（建筑物）条例》是一个好的开始，但香港还必须解决居民的经济困境和利益相关者之间的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:30:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/hong-kong-opinion/article/3259796/tougher-fire-safety-laws-hong-kong-wont-work-without-fixing-social-problems?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>智利对中国钢铁产品加征关税提振当地钢铁制造商CAP股价</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/world/americas/article/3259962/chiles-tariffs-chinese-steel-products-boost-local-steelmaker-caps-stock?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>周一上午，CAP 股价在圣地亚哥证券交易所上涨至 3.1%。此举对进口产品征收高达34%的反倾销费。 CAP决定暂停关闭钢厂的计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/world/americas/article/3259962/chiles-tariffs-chinese-steel-products-boost-local-steelmaker-caps-stock?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>德国因涉嫌为中国从事间谍活动而逮捕三人，英国则指控两人</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259959/germany-arrests-three-suspicion-spying-china-britain-charges-two?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>事态发展相隔数小时之际，一些欧洲国家首都对北京监控做法的威胁日益感到焦虑。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 16:35:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259959/germany-arrests-three-suspicion-spying-china-britain-charges-two?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着海外资本的观望，中国赢得投资的