cle/3259904/baidu-and-zhipu-ais-large-language-models-top-chinese-generative-ai-rankings-openai-anthropic-remain?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国最高军事指挥官承诺对海上争端的“不公正挑衅”进行报复</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3259942/top-chinese-military-commander-pledges-retaliate-against-unjust-provocation-over-maritime-disputes?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在青岛举行的海军研讨会上，解放军高级司令员张又侠呼吁在地区紧张局势升级之际进行对话并放弃“冷战思维”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3259942/top-chinese-military-commander-pledges-retaliate-against-unjust-provocation-over-maritime-disputes?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>台湾将拆除公共场所剩余蒋介石雕像</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3259936/taiwan-will-tear-down-all-remaining-statues-chiang-kai-shek-public-spaces?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>民进党政府表示，将迅速拆除统治该岛近三十年的760多座蒋介石雕像。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:02:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3259936/taiwan-will-tear-down-all-remaining-statues-chiang-kai-shek-public-spaces?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体就 TikTok“出售或禁止”法案猛烈抨击美国，而所有者字节跳动却保持沉默</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3259926/chinese-state-media-hit-out-us-over-tiktok-sell-or-ban-bill-owner-bytedance-remains-silent?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国官方媒体批评美国众议院通过的一项新法案，该法案将迫使 TikTok 撤资，而母公司字节跳动和北京方面却保持沉默。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3259926/chinese-state-media-hit-out-us-over-tiktok-sell-or-ban-bill-owner-bytedance-remains-silent?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家即将研制出激光推进超高速静音潜艇</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3259875/chinese-scientists-close-laser-propulsion-superfast-silent-submarines?utm_source=rss_feed</link><descript